<p style="font-family:Verdana" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2">&nbsp;</font></p>


<p style="font-family:Verdana" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2">Feat selection is next on the list of creating your
character, the feats you can choose from can give you extra attacks,
proficiencies with weapons you would otherwise be unable to use properly, extra
