</p>
<p style="font-family:Verdana" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><br></font>
</p>






<p style="font-family:Verdana" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2">Once you are finally happy with your character, it is time
to venture out into the world, and the makers of D&amp;D Online did an
excellent job at creating a newbie island that introduces a player to the
concepts of the game and rewards them for doing so, giving you a chance to
explore a dungeon, as well as take part in short tutorial quests designed with
