few quests that simply must be done to gain access to the city proper and begin
the bigger adventures.</font></p>


<font style="font-family:Verdana" size="2"><br></font>



<p style="font-family:Verdana" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2">The city is split up into several parts, each containing
their own quests oriented for certain level groups, including the docks, the
marketplace, and the Houses. Many of the quests you will find yourself
presented with can be approached with several strategies other than “Run
through and kill stuff,” though admittedly, that is likely what will happen in
