<p style="font-family:Verdana" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2">&nbsp;</font></p>


<p style="font-family:Verdana" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2">Also spread throughout these dungeons is of course monsters
to get in your way, or at least in the way of your blades if you choose to take
the quest on in a more combative fashion. The system of combat in D&amp;D
Online puts the player in a more active role, left- or right-clicking to swing
your weapons as well as giving you the option to block, jump back and forward,
